CET4 (ice creams) 

1. N-MASS Ice cream is a very cold sweet food made from frozen cream or a substance like cream and has a flavour such as vanilla, chocolate, or strawberry. 冰激凌 

例： I'll get you some ice cream. 我去给你拿些冰激凌。 

2. N-COUNT An ice cream is an amount of ice cream sold in a small container or a cone made of a thin wafer. (一客) 冰激凌; 冰激凌蛋卷 

例： Do you want an ice cream? 你想来个冰激凌吗？

